title: The Power of Words
itunes:title: The Power of Words
description:
Words can have all the power over you or no power over you, only you can decide that. In this episode, I am going to teach you how to take back your life by taking the power out of hurtful words from others.

 

Want to master your mindset? Every Monday I send out an email with mindset tips for the week, click here to receive that email: http://mondayemail.com/

Follow me on IG for more inspiration here: https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
